        <div class="simul-row"><span class="simul-lab">Frais professionnels remboursés</span><span class="simul-val">+ 200 €</span></div>
        <div class="simul-row"><span class="simul-lab">Base de rémunération brute</span><span class="simul-val">8 300 €</span></div>
